Introduced Version
HOUSE BILL No. 1274
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 27-2-30.
Synopsis: Insurance mandated gun free zone notices. Provides that an
insurer may not require an insured or prospective insured to post or
display a gun free zone notice. Prohibits an insurer from taking certain
actions based on the failure or refusal by an insured or prospective
insured to post or display a gun free zone notice. Specifies limitations.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Commons, Bascom, Greene, Ireland
January 6, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Insurance.
